      "instruction": "<p>Remove the skin from your<strong> smoked mackerel fillet[s] </strong>and discard, then add the <strong>skinned mackerel fillet[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>to the other side of the baking tray[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 6-7 min or until everything has warmed through – these are your <strong>golden chickpeas</strong> and <strong>warmed mackerel</strong></p>",
