    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>curry powder </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> to a heatproof bowl</p><p>Put the bowl in the<strong> microwave </strong>for 1-2 min or until the butter has melted<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>curried butter</strong></p>",
