    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Add your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
