    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spoon some of the <strong>curried butter</strong> over the <strong>warmed mackerel</strong> and tear into bite-sized pieces – this is your<strong> Indian-spiced</strong> <strong>mackerel</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed salad </strong>in bowls and top with the <strong>golden chickpeas</strong>, <strong>Indian-spiced</strong> <strong>mackerel </strong>and <strong>naan croutons</strong></p><p>Spoon over any <strong>remaining curried butter </strong>and dollop over the <strong>mango yoghurt</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
